### **🎯 COMPLIANCE FRAMEWORK**

#### **1. LAWFULNESS OF PROCESSING** ✅
```markdown
**Legal Basis**: Article 24(1) - Consent & Public Interest
- Student Identity Verification: Explicit consent obtained
- Fraud Detection: Legitimate public interest
- National Security: Legal obligation under Kenyan law

**Data Minimization**: Article 25(2)
- Only collect essential identity data
- Purpose limitation to verification only
- Automatic deletion after 5 years retention

**Accuracy Standards**: Article 26
- Real-time validation against government databases
- Automated error correction mechanisms
- Manual review override capabilities
```

#### **2. DATA SUBJECT RIGHTS** ✅
```markdown
**Right to Information**: Article 35
- Clear privacy notices at data collection
- Transparent processing purposes
- Access to all personal data categories

**Right to Access**: Article 36
- Self-service portal for data requests
- 30-day response time guarantee
- Free of charge access provisions

**Right to Rectification**: Article 37
- Online correction interface
- 15-day resolution timeline
- Verification of corrected data

**Right to Erasure**: Article 38
- "Right to be forgotten" implementation
- Automated deletion on request
- Third-party notification system

**Right to Data Portability**: Article 39
- Structured data export (JSON, XML, CSV)
- Machine-readable format provision
- Direct transmission to third parties
```

#### **3. TECHNICAL & ORGANIZATIONAL MEASURES** ✅
```markdown
**Encryption Standards**: Article 41
- AES-256 encryption at rest
- TLS 1.3 encryption in transit
- End-to-end encryption for biometric data
- Key rotation every 90 days

**Access Control**: Article 42
- Multi-factor authentication (MFA)
- Role-based access control (RBAC)
- Principle of least privilege
- Session timeout after 15 minutes

**Data Integrity**: Article 43
- Blockchain-based audit trails
- Immutable transaction logs
- Tamper-evident storage
- Regular integrity checks

**Security Monitoring**: Article 44
- 24/7 security operations center
- Real-time threat detection
- Automated incident response
- Quarterly penetration testing
```

