#### **BIOMETRIC DATA PROTECTION** ✅
```markdown
**Special Category Data**: Article 46
- Enhanced protection for biometric templates
- Separate storage from personal data
- Template hashing with salt
- One-way cryptographic transformation

**Template Security**:
- Liveness detection prevents spoofing
- Anti-spoofing algorithms
- Template distortion detection
- Continuous monitoring for anomalies
```

#### **CONSENT MANAGEMENT** ✅
```markdown
**Granular Consent**: Article 47
- Purpose-specific consent collection
- Granular opt-in/opt-out mechanisms
- Easy consent withdrawal
- Consent history tracking

**Consent Records**:
- Immutable consent blockchain
- Timestamp-verified consent
- Machine-readable consent format
- Audit-ready consent trails
```

